Package: chunkloader
Version: ${VERSION}
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: ${ARCH}
Maintainer: Sn0wAlice <github@sn0w.io>
Homepage: https://github.com/Sn0wAlice/chunkloader
Description: Dump webpack / Next.js / Framer / Flutter JS chunks and assets for analysis
 chunkloader takes a domain or a JS entry URL, discovers every referenced
 chunk or asset, and downloads them into a local folder for offline analysis.
 It handles webpack and Next.js chunk maps (including __BUILD_MANIFEST),
 native ESM bundles (Framer / rolldown / rollup / Vite) by recursively
 crawling the import graph, and Flutter web apps by reading the
 flutter_service_worker.js resource manifest.
